# Release Notes

## Version v0.1
- Initial implementation
- User creation and authentication
- Showing a list of activities
- Adding a new activity
- Displaying details of an activity

## Version v0.2
- Automated filling of Person field when adding a new activity
- Activity templates with associated experience points
- Improved UI

## Version v0.3.1
- Support for job requests

## Version v0.3.2
- Fixed bugs related to job requests
- Added relationships between activities and job requests
- Added job request status (completed or not)
- Improved navigation

## Version v0.4.1
- Leaderboards